        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[Schrodinger’s Call second trailer]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/07/schrodingers-call-second-trailer</link>
            <guid>https://www.resetera.com/threads/schrodinger%E2%80%99s-call-second-trailer.1233498/</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div><p>Publisher <a title="Companies > Shueisha Games [40 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/shueisha-games">Shueisha Games</a> and developer <a title="Companies > Acrobatic Chirimenjako" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/acrobatic-chirimenjako">Acrobatic Chirimenjako</a> have <a href="https://prtimes.jp/main/html/rd/p/000000089.000116303.html" target="_blank">released</a> the second trailer for spirit <a title="Genres > Adventure [2,379 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/adventure">adventure game</a> <em><a title="Games > Schrodinger's Call" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/schrodingers-call">Schrodinger’s Call</a></em>. <span id="more-977321"></span></p><p>The game will also be playable at BitSummit the 13th, which will run from July 18 to 20 at Miyako Messe in Kyoto, Japan.</p><p>Here is an overview of the game, via its <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2090390/Schrdingers_Call/" target="_blank">Steam page</a>:</p><blockquote><p><strong>About</strong></p><p>I am Mary. The last person in the world you’ll ever talk to. <em>Schrodinger’s Call</em> is an adventure game that uses a mysterious phone to connect with souls who cannot die. The main character, Mary, wakes up in a strange room with no memory. The player, along with the bewildered Mary, will save souls.</p><p>In a world devoid of human life, you awaken as Mary, the last ear to listen, the last voice to speak.</p><!-- AD: content -->
        <p>Forsaken souls seek your help over numerous calls, in a desperate attempt to regain the feelings they’ve lost.</p><p>You are Mary, the last voice they hear, unraveling lost souls with just a telephone.</p><p>Souls bound with strong regrets suffer somewhere between the lands of the living and the dead, desperately waiting for someone willing to listen. Will you be that ear and voice?</p><p><strong>How to Play</strong></p><p>Choose the words you want to speak to the souls who cannot die and the actions you want to take to save them and advance the story.</p><p>Calling various souls and gathering information is the key to moving forward.</p></blockquote><p><em>Schrodinger’s Call</em> is due out for <a title="Platforms > PC [23,610 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2090390/Schrdingers_Call/" target="_blank">Steam</a> in 2026.</p><p>Watch the trailer below.</p><h2><span>Trailer #2</span></h2><p><strong>Japanese</strong></p><p><iframe title="シュレディンガーズ・コール 2nd PV" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/e7wP-HpNydc?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p></div></div><br/><br/>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/07/schrodingers-call-second-trailer]]></content:encoded>
        </item>
